  <section id="summary">
    <div class="section-head"><span class="section-num">01</span><h2>Summary</h2></div>
    <p class="lede">Software developer with an MCA and BCA, and hands-on project experience across Python, Java, SQL, and web technologies including Django and Bootstrap. Built academic and internship projects spanning database-driven systems, blockchain-based threat detection, data analysis, and full-stack web applications — with a strong grounding in SDLC, OOP, and DBMS concepts.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="skills">
    <div class="section-head"><span class="section-num">02</span><h2>Technical Skills</h2></div>
    <dl class="skill-grid">
      <div class="skill-block"><dt>Languages</dt><dd>Python, Java, C, JavaScript</dd></div>
