      <div class="skill-block"><dt>Tools &amp; Platforms</dt><dd>VS Code, Jupyter Notebook, MySQL Workbench, Git</dd></div>
      <div class="skill-block"><dt>Operating Systems</dt><dd>Windows, Linux</dd></div>
    </dl>
  </section>

  <section id="experience">
    <div class="section-head"><span class="section-num">03</span><h2>Internship Experience</h2></div>
    <div class="entry">
      <div class="entry-tag">Robomanthan</div>
      <div>
        <h3>Software Development Intern</h3>
        <div class="sub">Project: Dynamic Food Ordering App</div>
        <ul>
          <li>Built a full-stack food ordering web application using Django (Python), Bootstrap, and MySQL, covering menu browsing, cart management, and order placement.</li>
          <li>Implemented backend logic for order processing and data handling, applying SDLC practices from requirement analysis through deployment.</li>
          <li>Collaborated within a small team to design responsive front-end interfaces with HTML, CSS, and Bootstrap.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="projects">
    <div class="section-head"><span class="section-num">04</span><h2>Academic Projects</h2></div>

    <div class="entry">
      <div class="entry-tag">MCA Project</div>
      <div>
        <h3>Adaptive Cyber Threat Detection Using Blockchain Analytics</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Designed an academic model applying blockchain principles — integrity, transparency, tamper-resistant logging — to detect and analyze cyber threats.</li>
          <li>Applied cybersecurity fundamentals and secure data handling practices to structure threat analysis logic.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="entry">
      <div class="entry-tag">BCA Project</div>
      <div>
        <h3>Cryptocurrency Price Prediction System</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Analyzed historical cryptocurrency price data using Python to identify trends and generate predictive insights.</li>
          <li>Applied data preprocessing and statistical analysis techniques to improve the reliability of predictions.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="entry">
      <div class="entry-tag">BCA Project</div>
      <div>
        <h3>Airline Ticket Reservation System</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Designed a database-driven reservation system in SQL handling flight search, seat availability, and booking records.</li>
          <li>Applied SDLC and data validation principles to ensure accurate, consistent booking data.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

